    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>So glad you liked the bread, Irina!  As for your question about holding the dough in the fridge, well, I&#39;m not totally sure what to tell you.  I&#39;m not terribly experienced in the world of bread doughs, and I haven&#39;t tried anything with this particular one beyond what&#39;s written in the recipe.  That said, though, I do think that if you put the dough into the fridge immediately after kneading it &#8211; before the yeast activates &#8211; that it should work.  Give it a go!</p>
    </div>

